Claude Desktop Buddy Pico
=========================

This project is a community fork of:

  Claude Desktop Buddy
  https://github.com/anthropics/claude-desktop-buddy
  Copyright (c) 2026 Anthropic, PBC
  Licensed under the MIT License.

The upstream repository provides the reference Hardware Buddy BLE protocol
and the original M5Stick-based firmware on which the buddy interaction model
in this fork is based. The port retargets that work onto the Raspberry Pi
Pico 2 W with a Pimoroni Pico Display Pack 2.8 and a LiPo SHIM.

This fork is an unofficial community build. It is not produced, endorsed,
or supported by Anthropic.

